{"_id":"kT3mNpQ7xW2vL9sR","name":"Academic Toolkit","type":"gear","img":"icons/tools/hand/pliers.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"A collection of notebooks, writing instruments, reference books, and measuring devices. Grants + to Academic Skill Challenges. Requires Skill Rank 4 to use effectively. Raw materials cost 25% of purchase price to craft (Homesteading Skill).","cost":25},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"bF8hJr5cYn4dG1oP","name":"Crafting Toolkit","type":"gear","img":"icons/tools/hand/pliers.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Small anvils, tables, kilns, or other large equipment — not easily mobile. Grants + to Crafting Skill Challenges. Requires Skill Rank 4 to use effectively. Raw materials cost 25% of purchase price to craft (Homesteading Skill).","cost":25},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"wX6tZq0iU3eMa7lK","name":"Expertise Toolkit","type":"gear","img":"icons/tools/hand/pliers.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Compasses, maps, lenses, and specialized tools; fits in a small satchel. Grants + to Expertise Skill Challenges. Requires Skill Rank 4 to use effectively. Raw materials cost 25% of purchase price to craft (Homesteading Skill).","cost":25},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"jS9nVc2gH5pB8kDf","name":"Magical Toolkit","type":"gear","img":"icons/tools/hand/pliers.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Channeling crystals, focusing diagrams, and etching chalk. Grants + to Magical Skill Challenges. Requires Skill Rank 4 to use effectively. Note: The Guild monitors all purchases of Magical Toolkits. Raw materials cost 25% of purchase price to craft (Homesteading Skill).","cost":50},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"rY4oIm7aT1uE6wNs","name":"Social Toolkit","type":"gear","img":"icons/tools/hand/pliers.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Cosmetics, wigs, and various perfumes. Grants + to Social Skill Challenges. Requires Skill Rank 4 to use effectively. Raw materials cost 25% of purchase price to craft (Homesteading Skill).","cost":25},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"dL2xFb9kP3cQ5vMh","name":"Training Toolkit","type":"gear","img":"icons/tools/hand/pliers.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Back braces, morphine, cleated shoes, and varied skill-specific training items. Grants + to Training Skill Challenges. Requires Skill Rank 4 to use effectively. Raw materials cost 25% of purchase price to craft (Homesteading Skill).","cost":25},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"nG7rA4tW1eP6bVm2","name":"20 Bullets/Shells","type":"gear","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/arrow.svg","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Standard bullets for firearms or shells for shotguns. Ammo Property: Bullet — can only be used with a firearm. Skill Req: 1. Price is per pack of 20 rounds.","cost":3},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"cH5yJ8dK3fO9xLs1","name":"20 Cavity Bullets","type":"gear","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/arrow.svg","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Bullets designed to expand on impact — extremely effective against unnatural targets. Ammo Properties: Bullet (firearm only), Cavity (gains + to Damage Flips against targets without an Armor value; Armor may still reduce damage to 0). Skill Req: 3. Price is per pack of 20.","cost":24},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"pB2mR6uN4wT7qZ0g","name":"20 Torch Bullets","type":"gear","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/arrow.svg","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Specially designed incendiary bullets commonly called 'flamers,' intended to light the walking dead on fire. Ammo Properties: Bullet (firearm only), Torch (characters who suffer Severe damage also gain Burning +1). Skill Req: 2. Price is per pack of 20.","cost":14},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"vE9sI3lD7cY2kA5h","name":"20 Wailer Bullets","type":"gear","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/arrow.svg","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Rock-salt shells or resin-wax bullets designed to incapacitate rather than kill. Ammo Properties: Bullet (firearm only), Wailer (imposes -- on Damage Flips but the attack gains the Stunning property). Skill Req: 2. Price is per pack of 20.","cost":6},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fX1nU8oG4tW6rM3p","name":"20 Arrows/Bolts","type":"gear","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/arrow.svg","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Standard arrows for bows or bolts for crossbows. Ammo Property: Bolt — can only be used with a Bow (Archery weapons). Skill Req: 1. Price is per pack of 20.","cost":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"gK7bL2eP9aS5mJ0v","name":"20 Piercing Arrows/Bolts","type":"gear","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/arrow.svg","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Arrowheads or bolt tips specially designed to punch through armor. Ammo Properties: Bolt (Bow weapons only), Piercing (if the target is wearing Armor, this weapon ignores 1 point of Armor when damaging). Skill Req: 1. Price is per pack of 20.","cost":5},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"hO4wQ3iF8nD6yT1r","name":"20 Barbed Arrows/Bolts","type":"gear","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/arrow.svg","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Arrowheads or bolt tips designed to tear at flesh when removed, making safe extraction difficult. Ammo Properties: Bolt (Bow weapons only), Barbed (a character wounded by this ammo suffers 1 damage at the end of any turn in which it spent 2 or more AP; removable with a TN 15 Doctor Challenge). Skill Req: 2. Price is per pack of 20.","cost":3},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"mC9tU7kR2xL5pA4g","name":"20 Piped Arrows/Bolts","type":"gear","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/arrow.svg","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Arrows or bolts with heads and shafts specially designed to channel blood from the wound. Ammo Properties: Bolt (Bow weapons only), Piped (if the target suffers Severe damage, it gains the Bleeding Out Condition). Skill Req: 2. Price is per pack of 20.","cost":5},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"sN6eH1bW9oI3vK8m","name":"5 Mortars","type":"gear","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/arrow.svg","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Explosive mortar rounds for use with the Mortar Gun only. Fires in an arc, allowing it to go over obstacles to reach targets. Ammo Property: Special (Mortar Gun) — can only be used with a Mortar Gun. Skill Req: 3. Price is per pack of 5 rounds.","cost":25},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"tP3yA5cZ7dF2uQ0x","name":"5 Darts","type":"gear","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/arrow.svg","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Small blowgun darts propelled by air. The dart itself is not especially dangerous — it is almost always coated in poison prior to firing. Ammo Property: Special (Blowgun) — can only be used with a Blowgun. Skill Req: 1. Price is per pack of 5 darts.","cost":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"wJ8kM4rB1hG6sE9n","name":"5 Grenades","type":"gear","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/arrow.svg","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Explosive grenade rounds for use with the Grenade Launcher only. Launches an explosive payload like a rifle bullet. Banned in Malifaux. Ammo Property: Special (Grenade Launcher) — can only be used with a Grenade Launcher. Skill Req: 3. Price is per pack of 5.","cost":20},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"xL5vO9pN2cT7mR3g","name":"1 Harpoon","type":"gear","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/arrow.svg","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"A heavy harpoon for use with the AG Harpoon Gun. Reusable if recovered. Cultists of December added a modification allowing a strong rope to be attached for reeling in struck targets. Ammo Property: Special (Harpoon Gun) — can only be used with a Harpoon Gun. Skill Req: 2.","cost":6},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"yF2sK6dW8bI4aH7q","name":"1 Fuel Tank","type":"gear","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/arrow.svg","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"A pressurized fuel canister providing approximately 10 shots for use with the Flamethrower only. The Flamethrower is a rare and notorious weapon; only the Freikorps have special permission to carry one legally. Ammo Property: Special (Flamethrower) — can only be used with a Flamethrower. Skill Req: 4.","cost":30},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"zQ9mA3tL1wP5eN6y","name":"Weapon Mod: Bayonet (Pistol)","type":"gear","img":"icons/equipment/weapon/sword-hilt.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"A small blade that attaches to a pistol at the barrel or around the grip (resembling bladed brass knuckles), allowing the gunslinger to defend herself in close quarters without holstering the pistol. Effect: Adds the Bayonet special property (melee attack option). Exclusive: Pistols only. To attach, total item Skill Req + existing mod Skill Reqs + this mod's Skill Req must not exceed the crafter's (Aspect + Crafting Skill Rank). Raw materials cost 25% of mod price to craft.","cost":3},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"aD7vJ4nG2rK8oS1b","name":"Weapon Mod: Bayonet (Rifle)","type":"gear","img":"icons/equipment/weapon/sword-hilt.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Small knife-like blades that attach to the end of a rifle, transforming it into a crude spear. Designed not to interfere with firing, but experienced marksmen dislike the extra weight pulling the tip down. Effect: Adds the Bayonet special property (melee attack option). Exclusive: Rifles only. To attach, total item Skill Req + existing mod Skill Reqs + this mod's Skill Req must not exceed the crafter's (Aspect + Crafting Skill Rank). Raw materials cost 25% of mod price to craft.","cost":4},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"bO5tE9cM7hF3xI2u","name":"Weapon Mod: Brutal","type":"gear","img":"icons/equipment/weapon/sword-hilt.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Reinforces or modifies the weapon to deliver crushing, brutal blows. Effect: The weapon gains the Brutal property (+  to its Damage Flip). Skill Req: 2. Cannot be applied to Finely Tuned weapons. To attach, total item Skill Req + existing mod Skill Reqs + this mod's Skill Req must not exceed the crafter's (Aspect + Crafting Skill Rank). Raw materials cost 25% of mod price to craft.","cost":15},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"cS1pB6aW4kL9vQ8r","name":"Weapon Mod: Custom Action","type":"gear","img":"icons/equipment/weapon/sword-hilt.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Customized action mechanism for a ranged weapon to extend its effective range. Effect: Increases range by +2. Exclusive: Ranged (z) weapons only. Skill Req: 1. Cannot be applied to Finely Tuned weapons. To attach, total item Skill Req + existing mod Skill Reqs + this mod's Skill Req must not exceed the crafter's (Aspect + Crafting Skill Rank). Raw materials cost 25% of mod price to craft.","cost":10},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"dM4gY2jH7sN5bT0e","name":"Weapon Mod: Custom Grip","type":"gear","img":"icons/equipment/weapon/sword-hilt.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"A bespoke grip fitted to a ranged weapon, improving accuracy and control. Effect: The weapon gains the Accurate property (+ to attack flips). Exclusive: Ranged (z) weapons only. Skill Req: 2. Cannot be applied to Finely Tuned weapons. To attach, total item Skill Req + existing mod Skill Reqs + this mod's Skill Req must not exceed the crafter's (Aspect + Crafting Skill Rank). Raw materials cost 25% of mod price to craft.","cost":20},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"eI8fK3uD1mO6wA9c","name":"Weapon Mod: Embellishment","type":"gear","img":"icons/equipment/weapon/sword-hilt.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Purely cosmetic modification — engraving, inlays, gilding, custom grips, decorative motifs, and so on. No mechanical effect; adds aesthetic value only. Skill Req: 0. Cost varies depending on complexity and artistry. Cannot be applied to Finely Tuned weapons.","cost":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fN7oL5tB9eP2aX4k","name":"Weapon Mod: Enlarged","type":"gear","img":"icons/equipment/weapon/sword-hilt.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"The weapon's striking head or blade is enlarged for greater damage output. Effect: Increases damage by 1/1/2 (Weak/Moderate/Severe). Exclusive: Melee (y) weapons only. Skill Req: 2. Cannot be applied to Finely Tuned weapons. To attach, total item Skill Req + existing mod Skill Reqs + this mod's Skill Req must not exceed the crafter's (Aspect + Crafting Skill Rank). Raw materials cost 25% of mod price to craft.","cost":7},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"gA2mS8cJ4rF7vH6y","name":"Weapon Mod: Extended","type":"gear","img":"icons/equipment/weapon/sword-hilt.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"The weapon's handle, shaft, or chain is lengthened to increase reach. Effect: Increases range by +1. Exclusive: Melee (y) weapons only. Skill Req: 2. Cannot be applied to Finely Tuned weapons. To attach, total item Skill Req + existing mod Skill Reqs + this mod's Skill Req must not exceed the crafter's (Aspect + Crafting Skill Rank). Raw materials cost 25% of mod price to craft.","cost":5},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"hV6pW1dI9oU3tK5z","name":"Weapon Mod: Folded Steel","type":"gear","img":"icons/equipment/weapon/sword-hilt.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"The blade is painstakingly re-forged using a folded steel technique, increasing edge quality and impact severity. Effect: Increases damage by 0/0/1 (Severe only) and grants the Brutal property (+ to Damage Flip). Exclusive: Melee (y) weapons only. Skill Req: 2. Cannot be applied to Finely Tuned weapons. To attach, total item Skill Req + existing mod Skill Reqs + this mod's Skill Req must not exceed the crafter's (Aspect + Crafting Skill Rank). Raw materials cost 25% of mod price to craft.","cost":10},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"iX3rC7lQ5nM2gE8a","name":"Weapon Mod: Grapeshot Barrel","type":"gear","img":"icons/equipment/weapon/sword-hilt.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Attaches a secondary single-shot barrel loaded with grapeshot to a firearm, providing an emergency close-range blast. Effect: Adds a barrel with a single grapeshot round — Range 5, Shotgun, Damage 1/2B/4B, Capacity 1, Reload 2 AP. Skill Req: 2. Cannot be applied to Finely Tuned weapons. To attach, total item Skill Req + existing mod Skill Reqs + this mod's Skill Req must not exceed the crafter's (Aspect + Crafting Skill Rank). Raw materials cost 25% of mod price to craft.","cost":20},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"jT9hN4vB8kY1fO3s","name":"Weapon Mod: Nickel-Plated","type":"gear","img":"icons/equipment/weapon/sword-hilt.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"The weapon is coated in a layer of polished nickel, giving it a distinctive gleaming appearance and mild resistance to corrosion. Effect: Grants the Nickel-Plated property (see GM for specific narrative benefits). Skill Req: 0. Cannot be applied to Finely Tuned weapons. To attach, total item Skill Req + existing mod Skill Reqs + this mod's Skill Req must not exceed the crafter's (Aspect + Crafting Skill Rank). Raw materials cost 25% of mod price to craft.","cost":15},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"kW2aG6mS0cL7nP9e","name":"Weapon Mod: Shoddy","type":"gear","img":"icons/equipment/weapon/sword-hilt.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"The weapon is deliberately constructed with cheap materials or poor workmanship, reducing its cost but limiting its potential. Effect: The weapon gains the Shoddy property — it cannot declare Triggers. Cost: Reduces the weapon's purchase price by 25% (this mod has no material cost; apply as a discount when purchasing or crafting). Skill Req: 0. Cannot be applied to Finely Tuned weapons.","cost":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lY5oJ3tV8dQ1xR4b","name":"Weapon Mod: Shortened","type":"gear","img":"icons/equipment/weapon/sword-hilt.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"The barrel or blade is cut down, making the weapon more concealable at the cost of some range. Effect: Reduces range by -1 (minimum 1 yard) and grants the Concealable property (+ to attempts to hide the weapon). Skill Req: 1. Cannot be applied to Finely Tuned weapons. To attach, total item Skill Req + existing mod Skill Reqs + this mod's Skill Req must not exceed the crafter's (Aspect + Crafting Skill Rank). Raw materials cost 25% of mod price to craft.","cost":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"mB8kH1sN6gW4pZ7f","name":"Weapon Mod: Throwing","type":"gear","img":"icons/equipment/weapon/sword-hilt.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"The weapon is rebalanced and fitted with a throwing grip or fin for accurate throwing. Effect: Reduces range by -1 (minimum 1 yard) and grants the Thrown property (if thrown, range is 3 yards + (3 x Thrown Weapons Skill rank)). Exclusive: Melee (y) weapons only. Skill Req: 1. Cannot be applied to Finely Tuned weapons. To attach, total item Skill Req + existing mod Skill Reqs + this mod's Skill Req must not exceed the crafter's (Aspect + Crafting Skill Rank). Raw materials cost 25% of mod price to craft.","cost":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"nF4vA9mT2rO5cK1e","name":"Binoculars","type":"gear","img":"icons/containers/bags/pack-simple-leather.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"A pair of optical binoculars for viewing distant objects. Essential equipment for scouts, hunters, and anyone who needs to observe from a safe distance. Standard adventuring gear in Malifaux.","cost":6},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"oK7sB3pL8wH6mN2d","name":"Blanket (Wool)","type":"gear","img":"icons/containers/bags/pack-simple-leather.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"A sturdy wool blanket for warmth in the field. Essential camping gear for those traveling through Malifaux's harsh wilderness or the cold Northern Hills.","cost":2},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"pH1tW6gI4aF9yV3c","name":"Canteen","type":"gear","img":"icons/containers/bags/pack-simple-leather.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"A portable water container for carrying drinking water in the field. Standard adventuring supply for travel through Malifaux's wilds.","cost":0.3},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"qI9nE2dM7vS5rK0b","name":"Haversack","type":"gear","img":"icons/containers/bags/pack-simple-leather.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"A sturdy canvas or leather bag worn over one shoulder, designed to carry a day's supplies and gear. Popular with soldiers, travelers, and adventurers across Malifaux.","cost":1.2},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"rL5gQ8bP1tO4fA7n","name":"Journal","type":"gear","img":"icons/containers/bags/pack-simple-leather.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"A blank book of quality paper for recording notes, sketches, maps, and observations. Invaluable for academics, reporters, and Fated tracking their Destiny Steps.","cost":2},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"sO3kT6mV9wJ2cG1p","name":"Kerosene (12 oz.)","type":"gear","img":"icons/containers/bags/pack-simple-leather.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"A 12-ounce container of kerosene fuel, used for lamps, heaters, and fire-starting. An essential supply for underground exploration or extended camping in Malifaux's darker regions.","cost":0.5},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"tM8aR4pN3hL7sI2w","name":"Rope (Hemp, 50 ft.)","type":"gear","img":"icons/containers/bags/pack-simple-leather.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Fifty feet of sturdy hemp rope. Useful for climbing, securing prisoners, rigging traps, lowering equipment, or a dozen other tasks an adventurer in Malifaux might encounter. Hemp is heavier but more affordable than silk rope.","cost":2.6},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"uB1fK9oG5vW2dE6r","name":"Rope (Silk, 50 ft.)","type":"gear","img":"icons/containers/bags/pack-simple-leather.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Fifty feet of lightweight, strong silk rope. Lighter and more compact than hemp rope, making it preferred by climbers and infiltrators. Slightly more expensive due to import costs through the Breach.","cost":2.9},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"vC6mJ3sA8tH1nQ4l","name":"Telescope","type":"gear","img":"icons/containers/bags/pack-simple-leather.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"A collapsible optical telescope for observing distant objects. Provides greater magnification than binoculars at greater range, useful for surveillance, navigation, and studying the strange celestial phenomena visible from Malifaux.","cost":2},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"wE9pF7kO2lB5aT3m","name":"Tent","type":"gear","img":"icons/containers/bags/pack-simple-leather.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"A portable canvas shelter providing protection from the elements. Essential for extended overland travel in Malifaux, where the dangers of sleeping in the open range from mundane weather to supernatural hazards.","cost":4},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"xN4gV1rS6mK9cI8o","name":"Valise","type":"gear","img":"icons/containers/bags/pack-simple-leather.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"A small, sturdy travel bag for carrying personal effects, documents, and supplies. More refined than a haversack; appropriate for professionals and socialites traveling through Malifaux City or beyond.","cost":0.8},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"yS7hL4wP3fG8bM2j","name":"Watch","type":"gear","img":"icons/containers/bags/pack-simple-leather.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"A quality pocket watch for keeping accurate time. In Malifaux, where the flow of time can be unpredictable and synchronizing with other Fated can be a matter of life and death, a reliable watch is more than a luxury.","cost":3},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"zA3tB9kN7mO1pL5e","name":"Pneumatic Augment: Enhanced Fist","type":"gear","img":"icons/equipment/hand/gauntlet-metal-grey.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Adds spiked protrusions, extra actuators, or springs to the pneumatic knuckles, allowing the recipient to punch significantly harder. Location: Arms limb only. Effect: Damaging +1 (Pugilism or Martial Arts attacks with this limb deal +1 additional damage). Slots Required: 2. Skill Req: 2. Note: Price does not include the pneumatic limb itself. Fatemaster approval required.","cost":5},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"aB6oC2wV8sE4rH9g","name":"Pneumatic Augment: Crusher","type":"gear","img":"icons/equipment/hand/gauntlet-metal-grey.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Replaces the pneumatic hand with an oversized fist and additional actuators. Can crush granite and bend steel; the limb becomes bulky and misshapen. Location: Arms limb only. Effect: Damaging +2 (Pugilism or Martial Arts attacks with this limb deal +2 additional damage). Slots Required: 3. Skill Req: 3. Note: Price does not include the pneumatic limb itself. Fatemaster approval required.","cost":30},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"bL9dG5pA3mK7tF1n","name":"Pneumatic Augment: Military Brace","type":"gear","img":"icons/equipment/hand/gauntlet-metal-grey.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Accommodates any ranged weapon, permanently integrating it into the prosthetic (cannot be removed). Allows the wielder to use the integrated weapon as if it were in her hand at any time. Location: Arms limb only. Effect: Integrated (Ranged Combat weapon). Slots Required: 1. Skill Req: 1. Note: Price does not include the weapon itself. Fatemaster approval required.","cost":15},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"cN2hJ8gT6bW4aO7s","name":"Pneumatic Augment: Mercenary Brace","type":"gear","img":"icons/equipment/hand/gauntlet-metal-grey.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Incorporates a melee weapon into the prosthetic. On a full limb, the weapon may fold or retract when sheathed. Allows the wielder to use the integrated weapon as if it were in her hand at any time. Location: Arms limb only. Effect: Integrated (Close Combat weapon). Slots Required: 1. Skill Req: 1. Note: Price does not include the weapon itself. Fatemaster approval required.","cost":15},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"dP7kI1mL9fS3vE2r","name":"Pneumatic Augment: Piston Driver","type":"gear","img":"icons/equipment/hand/gauntlet-metal-grey.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"A series of pistons and bone anchors adding explosive strength to the limb. Useful for physical labor such as rail laying or construction. Once per session per limb, increase Might Aspect by +5 until the start of her next turn. Location: Arms or Legs. Effect: Pneumatic (Might) — once per session, +5 Might until start of next turn. Slots Required: 1. Skill Req: 2. Note: Price does not include the pneumatic limb itself. Fatemaster approval required.","cost":10},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"eR4nO6tA2bP8gK5w","name":"Pneumatic Augment: Steam Coils","type":"gear","img":"icons/equipment/hand/gauntlet-metal-grey.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Powerful industrial springs reset by the limb's pneumatics, enabling bursts of greatly increased movement speed. Accompanied by visible steam and hissing sounds — poor for stealth. Requires time to build pressure between uses. Location: Legs limb only. Effect: Pneumatic (Speed) — once per session, +5 Speed until start of next turn. Slots Required: 1. Skill Req: 2. Note: Price does not include the pneumatic limb itself. Fatemaster approval required.","cost":10},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fS1vM7cJ4rW9eB3n","name":"Pneumatic Augment: Trade Custom","type":"gear","img":"icons/equipment/hand/gauntlet-metal-grey.webp","system":{"quantity":1,"description":"Incorporates a skill toolkit into the prosthetic design. Tools can be internalized or attached externally, folding flat against the limb when not in use. Allows the wielder to use the integrated toolkit as if it were in her hand at any time. Location: Any pneumatic limb. Effect: Integrated (Toolkit). Slots Required: 1. Skill Req: 1. Note: Price does not include the toolkit itself. Fatemaster approval required.","cost":2},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{},"flags":{}}
